org.ggp.base.util.propnet.factory.annotater

Class PropNetAnnotater

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ggp.base.util.propnet.factory.annotater.PropNetAnnotater

  • public class PropNetAnnotater
extends java.lang.Object
    Annotater generates ( base ?x ) annotations that explicitly specify the domains of the propositions in a game. This only works on some relatively simple games, unfortunately.
    Author:
    Ethan Dreyfuss
